Detailed Description

Represents a status update from a Twitter user.

The most important components of this object are the GetText() and GetUser() methods.

const wxString& TwitterStatus::GetSource (  )  const [inline]

Returns the source (where it was posted from).

This usually contains 'web' (for tweets from the website), 'txt' (for text message tweets) or a third party application name (like 'twittle') with an embedded link to the application website.
